Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,淚雨的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的特別 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在這個樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有會輸的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放狀態持續時間過長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就會漸漸地被咒印給侵蝕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被侵蝕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會永遠失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經沒時間再磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手的感覺…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也伴隨著風險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱做終結之穀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此為舞臺不是正合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過閒聊已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多也該做個終結了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止的戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下麵是第七班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春野櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鳴人在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和佐助在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少別拖我的後腿哦 廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為因為因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你說過啊 所以這傢伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是三人小組嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我們三個是一個集體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧 膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧 膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你戰鬥一場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想要和你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想眼睜睜地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著重要的同伴死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是笑呢 是興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到能跟你在這裏決鬥並且取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖後腿的居然也如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會一輩子都當拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交手之前 把護額戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 快點戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有本事弄傷我的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們作為木葉忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對等決鬥的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味不會消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是來遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能及時趕到 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定拼盡了全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起的時候 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸總是會提到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我是獨一無二的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為你必須超越的壁壘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和你一起共存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被你憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萬花筒寫輪眼的開眼者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那需要特殊的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉自己最親密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結之穀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和佐助竟然在這裏戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠諷刺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著這條河流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛讓我目睹了一場永無止盡的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像建造了木葉村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化身為這兩尊石像的人的命運一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這兩人一息尚存…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉自己最親密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會按你說的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己的方法獲得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己的方法…超越你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這驟雨 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑氣味已經無法追蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 比起去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是鳴人更為優先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過會把佐助帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一生的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一切都還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會信守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是常說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這就是我的忍道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能信守的約定
